name: High Roller (BeanWare Games)
description:
You play as a dice, try and navigate the casino themed level, pick up chips and get to the end.

You'll battle a craps table, Barstool Bounce, a card waterfall, and end with the slot machine mayhem!

WASD to move, ESC to return to menu, R to reset.

All 3D models were made during the jam!
